description: The Marni collection is a mix of Italian refinement and experimental sophistication. Despite having no formal training, when the Consuelo Castiglioni launched the brand in 1994 it was an immediate success. A family run business for over 20 years, the small but iconic maison has a cult following. These colour block optical glasses from Marni are crafted from acetate and feature a two tone pink and black design and a tortoiseshell effect. Straight arms with angled tips and a brand logo to the internal arm complete these striking glasses.

description: Some of our favorite people are bounty hunters. So much so, in fact, that we decided to put one on a neck tie. Honor the legacy of The Mandalorian with this navy and cyan blue plaid check tie, featuring Mando's iconic helmet.

name: Boss Men's Bright Red Tie
description: A contemporary tie by Boss. Crafted in Italy from a blend that is rich in silk, this three-inch tie features a jacquard-woven dot pattern. Elevate formal looks with this accessory.

name: printed bow tie
description: Brown silk printed bow tie from Fef猫.

name: Star Wars Bb-8 and Dio Boy's Tie
description: Friends forever, the two friendliest droids in the Empire come together on this classic woven 100% silk boy's tie. Bb-8 and Dio whoosh around over the surface, separated only by slim pale blue accent lines. Officially licensed by Lucasfilm Ltd.

name: Game of Thrones Stark Geometric Sword Men's Tie
description: A beautiful blue tie with Dire Wolf sigils over a geometric pattern of swords would make even Arya stark envious. Made of woven silk, this tie will have you feeling cooler than the snowfall in Winterfell.

name: Tommy Hilfiger Men's Slim Dog Tie
description: Showcasing adorable dogs decked out in stars and stripes, this slim tie from Tommy Hilfiger is a salute to celebratory style.

description: Keep your holiday formalwear game on point with this classic silk tie from Tommy Hilfiger, adorned with adorable polar bears and Christmas trees to help you lock in those good-time festive vibes.

name: Boss Men's Dark Pink Tie
description: A modern tie by Boss, crafted in Italy from recycled material for a more responsible approach to production. This two-inch tie is jacquard woven with a diagonal stripe to add colorful detail to plain tailoring. Choose it to elevate formal looks with a touch of Boss flair.

name: Tommy Hilfiger Men's Coastline Stripe Skinny Tie
description: Sunday marina, weekday office, weeknight dinner out. Look smart with the classic stripes of Tommy Hilfiger's Coastline skinny tie.

name: Star Wars R2D2 Paisley Men's Tie
description: Fine gold-like and silver-like thread are interwoven against a space-black backdrop on this 100% silk tie. Featuring the likeness of everyone's favorite droid R2D2, and set in a large paisley pattern, this tie is sure to become your next favorite accessory. Officially licensed by Lucasfilm Ltd.

description: A woven look in a vibrant blue colorway gives this tie from Tommy Hilfiger an element of distinction, one that will perfectly complement a more formal look.
